      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering its signature high-revving power through individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure mechanical longevity, the subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system has been recently overhauled. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback these chassis are known for. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and the compression is within factory tolerances. A mechanically sound specimen ready for the backroads.",
